# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your real Formspree form ID.
# .env.local is already gitignored — never commit real values.

# 1. Sign up free at https://formspree.io and create a new form
# 2. Set the notification email to wherever you want feedback to land
# 3. Copy the form ID from your endpoint, which looks like:
#      https://formspree.io/f/abcd1234
#    The ID is the "abcd1234" part — put it below, no quotes, no slashes.
# 4. Also add this same variable in Vercel: Project -> Settings -> Environment Variables
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID=
